According to Wikipedia, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seth_Low" rel="nofollow">Seth Low</a> was &quot;an American educator and political figure who served as mayor of Brooklyn, as President of Columbia University, as diplomatic representative of the United States, and as Mayor of New York City.&quot;

&quot;Mrs. C. S. Whitman&quot; is <a href="http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&amp;GRid=61246688" rel="nofollow">Olive Hitchcock Whitman</a>, the wife of New York Governor <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_S._Whitman" rel="nofollow">Charles Whitman</a>. 

<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lorillard_Spencer" rel="nofollow">Lorillard Spencer</a> was &quot;Military Secretary to New York Governor Charles Seymour Whitman.&quot;
